Class Properties

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Dictionary<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
      • org.jruyi.common.Properties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>, IDumpable

    public final class Properties
extends java.util.Dictionary<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
implements java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>, java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable, IDumpable
    A substitution class to Hashtable to be used for Dictionary properties in OSGi, for synchronization is not necessary and does a penalty to the performance.
